BEGIN_PGML
The ratio of girls to boys in a preschool is [$girl] to [$boy]. If there are [$total] kids in the school, how many girls are there in the preschool?

[_]{$totalgirls}{10}

END_PGML

############################################################
# Solution
############################################################

BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
Let [`x`] be the number of girls in the preschool. We can represent this situation with the following proportion:

[`\frac{[$girl]}{[$girl]+[$boy]} = \frac{x}{[$total]}\text{.}`] Solve this equation for [`x\text{.}`]

END_PGML_SOLUTION

